                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220911-221-victim2088 t18220911-221-viclabel1179"></join> in partnership with Richard and John Lane. The prisoner was in our employ till the end of June. I gave him a coat to make about the beginning of June, and by mistake he was paid beforehand; it was never brought home; he was paid for it, as he said he had brought it back.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18220911-221-person2090">
                  CHARLES 
                  BENNETT
               <interp inst="t18220911-221-person2090" type="surname" value="BENNETT"></interp>
